          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Proton-induced nuclear reactions in neptunium-237",
                "targets. Production of plutonium tracers in the energy",
                "range 15-40 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "J.Aaltonen",
                "E.A.Gromova",
                "V.Jakovlev",
                "S.J.Heselius",
                "P.Dendooven",
                "W.Trzaska"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,RCA,88,129,2000",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,RCA,88,129,2000",
                    "doi": "10.1524/ract.2000.88.3-4.129",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "RCA",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "88",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "129"
                      },
                      "date": 2000
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "2SF HLS",
                "4RUSRI",
                "2SF ABA",
                "2SF JYV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2SF JYV"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A 40.1-MeV proton beam of the K-130",
                "Cyclotron for the thin target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "2SF ABA"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A 17-MeV proton beam 103-Cm Avf",
                "Cyclotron for the thick targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets of neptunium oxide (NpO(2)) were prepared by",
                "multiple thermal decomposition of neptunium nitrate",
                "cellulose painted on 10 mum and 50 mum thick aluminum",
                "backings. The average thickness of the Np-237O(2) layer",
                "was 120 mug/cm**2 for the thin targets and 2 mg/cm**2",
                "for the thick targets. The thickness variations were",
                "within 3% for both types of targets.  The average",
                "thicknesses were determined by weighing."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The alpha-activity of Pu-236 was measured with",
                "surface-barrier silicon detectors with sensitive areas",
                "of 200-mm**2 and an energy resolution of 30-keV at",
                " 5767-keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The beam current on the thin target was",
                "approximatelly 1 muA.  For the thick target the beam",
                "current was 7 muA."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The irradiation time was about 5 hours for thin",
                "target and 10 hours for thick target."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "STTA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Eight pairs of 237-Np oxide targets of 120 mu-g",
                "and aluminium foils of different thicknesses were",
                "mounted in a multiple target system."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "DECAY"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
